sentences.sentence: Bai Yun gave birth to a cub in 1999 after she was artificially inseminated. Her offspring, Hua Mei, is the first U.S.-born panda to survive into adolescence.
sentences.translation: “白云”在1999年接受人工受精后生下了一只幼仔，它就是“华美”，是第一只出生在美国并成长到青春期的大熊猫。
